{"word":"G2922 - κριτήριον - kritḗrion - kree-tay'-ree-on - To judge","slug":"G2922","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κριτήριον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>kritḗrion"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kree-tay'-ree-on"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>To judge"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03BA;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03C4;&#x03B7;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03B9;&#x03BF;&#x03BD; - krite&#x0304;rion</b> - <i>kree-tay'-ree-on</i><p/>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>; a <i>rule</i> of judging (&ldquo;criterion&rdquo;), that is, (by implication) a <i>tribunal:</i> - to judge, judgment (seat)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2632\">G2632</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}